他的职业生涯得到认可，是在Gerald Peary的记录片《{{le|电影之爱：美国电影批评史|For the Love of Movies: The Story of American Film Criticism}}》（For the Love of Movies: The Story of American Film Criticism）里，片中他解释了自己如何将作者论应用到希区柯克的《驚魂記》。谈及他与老对手宝琳·凯尔的论战时，他机敏地评论说：“我们彼此成就了对方，算是针锋相对。”<ref>[http://www.tcm.com/tcmdb/title.jsp?stid=775058 ''For the Love of Movies: The Story of American Film Criticism''] {{Wayback|url=http://www.tcm.com/tcmdb/title.jsp?stid=775058 |date=20200516023321 }} at the [[特纳经典电影频道|TCM Movie Database]]</ref>

此后他继续为《[[纽约观察家|纽约观察家]]》撰写电影评论，直至2009年。他同时担任哥伦比亚大学电影学教授一职，并于2011年退休，主要授课内容为：世界电影史、美国电影和希区柯克研究。他联合创办了[[國家影評人協會|美国电影评论协会]]，J. Hoberman<ref>{{cite news |author=J. Hoberman |url=http://www.villagevoice.com/2005-10-18/specials/get-reel/ |title=Get Reel |work=[[Village_Voice|Village Voice]] |date=2005-10-18 |accessdate=2011-02-23 |archive-date=2014-12-21 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20141221141213/http://www.villagevoice.com/2005-10-18/specials/get-reel/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>、Kenneth Turan<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.bfi.org.uk/sightandsound/feature/49480 |title=Sight & Sound; Critics On Critics |publisher=BFI |date=2010-03-25 |accessdate=2011-02-23 |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20110406021124/http://www.bfi.org.uk/sightandsound/feature/49480/ |archivedate=2011-04-06 }}</ref>、Armond White<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.filmmakermagazine.com/issues/winter2004/features/the_critic.php |title=THE CRITIC- Filmmaker Magazine – Winter 2004 |publisher=Filmmaker Magazine |date= |accessdate=2011-02-23 |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20110525234954/http://www.filmmakermagazine.com/issues/winter2004/features/the_critic.php |archivedate=2011-05-25 }}</ref>、Michael Phillips和AO Scott都曾表示受过他的影响。

萨里斯和影评家{{le|莫莉·哈斯凯尔|Molly Haskell}}在1969年结婚；他们在曼哈顿的[[上东城|上东城]]生活。<ref name=NYT/>

